  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0001",
          "zh": "阿柴虜吐谷渾，遼東鮮卑也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0002",
          "zh": "父弈洛韓，有二子，長曰吐谷渾，少曰若洛廆。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0003",
          "zh": "[1]若洛廆別為慕容氏。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0004",
          "zh": "渾庶長，廆正嫡。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0005",
          "zh": "父在時，分七百戶與渾，[2]渾與廆二部俱牧馬，馬鬭相傷，廆怒，遣信謂渾曰：「先公處分，與兄異部，牧馬何不相遠，而致鬭爭相傷？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0006",
          "zh": "」渾曰：「馬是畜生，食草飲水，春氣發動，所以致鬭。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0007",
          "zh": "鬭在於馬，而怒及人邪。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0008",
          "zh": "乖別甚易，今當去汝萬里。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0009",
          "zh": "」於是擁馬西行，日移一頓，頓八十里。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0010",
          "zh": "經數頓，廆悔悟，深自咎責，遣舊父老及長史乙那樓追渾令還。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0011",
          "zh": "[3]渾曰：「我乃祖以來，樹德遼右，又卜筮之言，先公有二子，福胙並流子孫。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0012",
          "zh": "我是卑庶，理無並大，今以馬致別，殆天所啟。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0013",
          "zh": "諸君試擁馬令東，馬若還東，我當相隨去。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0014",
          "zh": "」樓喜拜曰：「處可寒。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0015",
          "zh": "」虜言「處可寒」，宋言爾官家也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0016",
          "zh": "即使所從二千騎共遮馬令回，不盈三百步，欻然悲鳴突走，聲若頹山。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0017",
          "zh": "如是者十餘輩，一向一遠。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0018",
          "zh": "樓力屈，又跪曰：「可寒，此非復人事。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0019",
          "zh": "」渾謂其部落曰：「我兄弟子孫，並應昌盛，廆當傳子及曾孫玄孫，其間可百餘年，我乃玄孫間始當顯耳。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0020",
          "zh": "」於是遂西附陰山。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0021",
          "zh": "遭晉亂，遂得上隴。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0022",
          "zh": "後廆追思渾，作阿干之歌。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0023",
          "zh": "鮮卑呼兄為「阿干」。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0024",
          "zh": "廆子孫竊號，以此歌為輦後大曲。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0025",
          "zh": "渾既上隴，出罕幵、西零。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0026",
          "zh": "西零，今之西平郡，罕幵，今枹罕縣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0027",
          "zh": "自枹罕以東千餘里，暨甘松，西至河南，南界昴城、龍涸。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0028",
          "zh": "自洮水西南，極白蘭，數千里中，逐水草，廬帳居，以肉酪為糧。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0029",
          "zh": "西北諸雜種謂之為阿柴虜。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0030",
          "zh": "渾年七十二死，有子六十人，長吐延嗣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0031",
          "zh": "吐延身長七尺八寸，勇力過人，性刻暴，為昴城羌酋姜聰所刺，劍猶在體，呼子葉延，語其大將絕拔渥曰：[4]「吾氣絕，棺斂訖，便遠去保白蘭。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0032",
          "zh": "白蘭地既嶮遠，又土俗懦弱，易為控御。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0033",
          "zh": "葉延小，意乃欲授與餘人，恐倉卒終不能相制。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0034",
          "zh": "今以葉延付汝，汝竭股肱之力以輔之，孺子得立，吾無恨矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0035",
          "zh": "」抽劍而死。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0036",
          "zh": "嗣位十三年，年三十五。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0037",
          "zh": "有子十二人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0038",
          "zh": "葉延少而勇果，年十歲，縛草為人，號曰姜聰，每旦輒射之，射中則喜，不中則號叫泣涕。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0039",
          "zh": "其母曰：「讎賊諸將已屠膾之，汝年小，何煩朝朝自苦如此。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0040",
          "zh": "」葉延嗚咽不自勝，答母曰：「誠知無益，然葉延罔極之心，不勝其痛耳。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0041",
          "zh": "」性至孝，母病，三日不能食，葉延亦不食。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0042",
          "zh": "頗視書傳，自謂曾祖弈洛韓始封昌黎公，曰：「吾為公孫之子。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0043",
          "zh": "案禮，公孫之子，得氏王父字。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0044",
          "zh": "」命姓為吐谷渾氏。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0045",
          "zh": "嗣立二十三年，年三十三。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0046",
          "zh": "[5]有子四人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0047",
          "zh": "長子碎奚立。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0048",
          "zh": "碎奚性純謹，三弟專權，碎奚不能制，諸大將共誅之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0049",
          "zh": "碎奚憂哀不復攝事，遂立子視連為世子，委之事，號曰「莫賀郎」。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0050",
          "zh": "「莫賀」，宋言父也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0051",
          "zh": "碎奚遂以憂死。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0052",
          "zh": "在位二十五年，年四十二。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0053",
          "zh": "有子六人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0054",
          "zh": "子視連以父憂卒，不遊娛，不酣宴。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0055",
          "zh": "在位十五年，年四十二。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0056",
          "zh": "有子二人，長曰視羆，次烏紇提。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0057",
          "zh": "[6]視羆嗣立十一年，年四十二。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0058",
          "zh": "子樹洛干等並小，弟烏紇提立。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0059",
          "zh": "紇提立八年，年三十五。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0060",
          "zh": "視羆子樹洛干立，自稱車騎將軍，義熙初也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0061",
          "zh": "樹洛干死，弟阿犲自稱驃騎將軍。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0062",
          "zh": "譙縱亂蜀，阿犲遣其從子西彊公吐谷渾敕來泥拓土至龍涸、平康。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0063",
          "zh": "少帝景平中，阿犲遣使上表獻方物。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0064",
          "zh": "詔曰：「吐谷渾阿犲介在遐表，慕義可嘉，宜有寵任。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0065",
          "zh": "今酬其來款，可督塞表諸軍事、安西將軍、沙州刺史、澆河公。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0066",
          "zh": "」未及拜受，太祖元嘉三年，又詔加除命。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0067",
          "zh": "未至而阿犲死，弟慕璝立。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0068",
          "zh": "[7]六年，表曰：「大宋應運，四海宅心，臣亡兄阿犲慕義天朝，款情素著。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0069",
          "zh": "去年七月五日，謁者董湛至，宣傳明詔，顯授榮爵，而臣私門不幸，亡兄見背。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0070",
          "zh": "臣以懦弱，負荷後任，然天恩所報，本在臣門，若更反覆，懼停信命。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0071",
          "zh": "輒拜受寵任，奉遵上旨，伏願詳處，更授章策。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0072",
          "zh": "」七年，詔曰：「吐谷渾慕璝兄弟慕義，至誠可嘉，宜授策爵，以甄忠款。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0073",
          "zh": "可督塞表諸軍事、征西將軍、沙州刺史、隴西公。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0074",
          "zh": "先是晉末，金城東允街縣胡人乞伏乾歸擁部眾據洮河、罕幵，自號隴西公。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0075",
          "zh": "乾歸死，子熾磐立，遣使詣晉朝歸順，以為使持節、都督河西諸軍事、平西將軍，公如故。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0076",
          "zh": "高祖即位，進號安西大將軍。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0077",
          "zh": "熾磐死，子茂蔓立。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0078",
          "zh": "[8]慕璝前後屢遣軍擊，茂蔓率部落東奔隴右，慕璝據有其地。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0079",
          "zh": "是歲，赫連定於長安為索虜拓跋燾所攻，擁秦戶口十餘萬西次罕幵，欲向涼州，慕璝距擊，大破之，生擒定。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0080",
          "zh": "燾遣使求，慕璝以定與之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0081",
          "zh": "九年，慕璝遣司馬趙敍奉貢獻，幷言二萬人捷。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0082",
          "zh": "太祖加其使持節、散騎常侍、都督西秦河沙三州諸軍事、征西大將軍、西秦河二州刺史、領護羌校尉，進爵隴西王。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0083",
          "zh": "弟慕延為平東將軍，慕璝兄樹洛干子拾寅為平北將軍，阿豺子煒代鎮軍將軍。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0084",
          "zh": "詔慕璝南國將士，昔沒在佛佛者，並悉致。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0085",
          "zh": "慕璝遣送朱昕之等五十五戶，一百五十四人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0086",
          "zh": "慕璝死，弟慕延立，[9]遣使奉表。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0087",
          "zh": "十五年，除慕延使持節、散騎常侍、都督西秦河沙三州諸軍事、鎮西大將軍、領護羌校尉、西秦河二州刺史、隴西王。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0088",
          "zh": "十六年，改封河南王。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0089",
          "zh": "其年，以拾虔弟拾寅為平西將軍，慕延庶長子繁暱為撫軍將軍，慕延嫡子瑍為左將軍、河南王世子。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0090",
          "zh": "十九年，追贈阿豺本號安西、秦沙三州諸軍事、沙州刺史、領護羌校尉、隴西王。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0091",
          "zh": "索虜拓跋燾遣軍擊慕延，大破之，慕延率部落西奔白蘭，攻破于闐國。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0092",
          "zh": "慮虜復至，二十七年，遣使上表云：「若不自固者，欲率部曲入龍涸越嶲門。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0093",
          "zh": "」并求牽車，獻烏丸帽、女國金酒器、胡王金釧等物。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0094",
          "zh": "太祖賜以牽車，若虜至不自立，聽入越嶲。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0095",
          "zh": "虜竟不至也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0096",
          "zh": "慕延死，拾寅自立。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0097",
          "zh": "二十九年，以拾寅為使持節、督西秦河沙三州諸軍事、安西將軍、領護羌校尉、西秦河二州刺史、河南王。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0098",
          "zh": "拾寅東破索虜，加開府儀同三司。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0099",
          "zh": "世祖大明五年，拾寅遣使獻善舞馬，四角羊。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0100",
          "zh": "皇太子、王公以下上舞馬歌者二十七首。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0101",
          "zh": "太宗泰始三年，進號征西大將軍。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0102",
          "zh": "五年，拾寅奉表獻方物，以弟拾皮為平西將軍、金城公。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0103",
          "zh": "前廢帝又進號車騎大將軍。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0104",
          "zh": "其國西有黃沙，南北一百二十里，東西七十里，不生草木，沙州因此為號。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0105",
          "zh": "屈真川有鹽池，甘谷嶺北有雀鼠同穴，或在山嶺，或在平地，雀色白，鼠色黃，地生黃紫花草，便有雀鼠穴。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0106",
          "zh": "白蘭土出黃金、銅、鐵。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0107",
          "zh": "其國雖隨水草，大抵治慕賀川。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0108",
          "zh": "[10]",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0109",
          "zh": "史臣曰：吐谷渾逐草依泉，擅強塞表，毛衣肉食，取資佃畜，而錦組繒紈，見珍殊俗，徒以商譯往來，故禮同北面。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0110",
          "zh": "自昔哲王，雖存柔遠，要荒回隔，禮文弗被，大不過子，義著春秋。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0111",
          "zh": "晉、宋垂典，不修古則，遂爵班上等，秩擬台光。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0112",
          "zh": "辮髮稱賀，非尚簪冕，言語不通，寧敷袞職。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0113",
          "zh": "雖復苞篚歲臻，事惟賈道，金罽氈毦，非用斯急，送迓煩擾，獲不如亡。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0114",
          "zh": "若令肅慎年朝，越裳歲饗，固不容以異見書，取高前策。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0115",
          "zh": "聖人謂之荒服，此言蓋有以也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0116",
          "zh": "校勘記",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0117",
          "zh": "父弈洛韓有二子長曰吐谷渾少曰若洛廆 「弈洛韓」御覽一二一引十六國春秋前燕錄、晉書、通典作「涉歸」。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0118",
          "zh": "「若洛廆」前燕錄作「弈洛瓌」。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0119",
          "zh": "分七百戶與渾 晉書吐谷渾傳作一千七百家。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0120",
          "zh": "遣舊父老及長史乙那樓追渾令還 「乙那樓」晉書作「那樓馮」。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0121",
          "zh": "按魏書官氏志，一那蔞氏後改為蔞氏。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0122",
          "zh": "乙那樓蓋一那蔞之異譯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0123",
          "zh": "宋書但稱其姓，晉書則著其名曰馮。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0124",
          "zh": "下云「樓喜拜曰」，沈約蓋誤以乙那為姓，樓為其名。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0125",
          "zh": "語其大將絕拔渥曰 「絕拔渥」魏書作「紇拔渥」，晉書作「紇拔泥」。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0126",
          "zh": "嗣立二十三年年三十三 「年三十三」各本並作「年四十三」，據晉書改。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0127",
          "zh": "按上云年十歲，父死，此云嗣立二十三年，則當作年三十三。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0128",
          "zh": "有子二人長曰視羆次烏紇提 晉書同。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0129",
          "zh": "魏書吐谷渾傳以視羆為視連之弟。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0130",
          "zh": "未至而阿犲死弟慕璝立 據魏書吐谷渾傳，慕璝為阿犲兄子，非其弟。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0131",
          "zh": "宋書載慕璝表云「臣亡兄阿犲慕義天朝」，則沈書稱慕璝為阿犲之弟，或有所據。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0132",
          "zh": "子茂蔓立 「茂蔓」御覽一二七引十六國春秋西秦錄、魏書、晉書、通鑑並作「暮末」。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0133",
          "zh": "通典邊防典作「茙蔓」。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0134",
          "zh": "本注云：「茙音戎。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0135",
          "zh": "弟慕延立 「慕延」十六國春秋作「末利延」，魏書作「慕利延」。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0136",
          "zh": "大抵治慕賀川 「慕賀川」各本並作「慕賀州」，南齊書作「慕駕川」。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0137",
          "zh": "魏書吐谷渾傳原卷亡，北史吐谷渾傳作「伏羅川」。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0138",
          "zh": "通典邊防典亦作「伏羅川」。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0139",
          "zh": "「伏羅川」即「慕賀川」之異譯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0140",
          "zh": "「州」則為「川」字之譌，今改正。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}